{
  "name": "Ink Clone",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Non%20Elemental.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You infuse chakra into the ink as you then infuse a chakra seal into it. You conjure a clone of yourself made of ink. They look, sound and act as your describe. The cost of these clones cannot be reduced below half. An Ink clone has 1 Hit point and can be no farther than<br />90 feet from you. It can walk, talk and interact with things but it cannot declare an attack. This clone acts at the end of your turn. As a bonus action you can command the clone to attack. When you do it pretends to weave hand seals to cast a jutsu targeting a single creature within 60 feet of it.</p><p>The target creature makes a Wisdom (Insight) Check vs your Ninjutsu Save DC. On a failure, they become distracted by the clones antics. A creature distracted in this manner grants the next attack targeting it advantage and they are treated as surprised against this attack.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
